<h2>🛡 About Defence</h2>

<p style="line-height:1.8;">
A career in Defence offers the opportunity to serve the nation with pride. You can join the Indian Army, Navy, Air Force, Coast Guard, or Defence Research organizations through various entry routes after school or graduation.
</p>

