<div class="card">

<h2>🎓 Entry Routes</h2>

<ul>
<li>NDA</li>
<li>CDS</li>
<li>AFCAT</li>
<li>Indian Navy Entry</li>
<li>Indian Coast Guard</li>
<li>Technical Entry Scheme (TES)</li>
<li>SSC Technical</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>🗺️ Career Roadmap</h2>

<ul>
<li>✅ Complete 10th</li>
<li>✅ Complete 12th (PCM Preferred)</li>
<li>✅ Prepare for NDA / AFCAT / CDS</li>
<li>✅ Written Examination</li>
<li>✅ SSB Interview</li>
<li>✅ Medical Test</li>
<li>✅ Defence Academy Training</li>
<li>✅ Become Defence Officer</li>
</ul>

